OL,3,CHospital declares critical incident
OL,4,Cwith patients waiting up to 50 hours
OL,6,FRoyal Liverpool Hospital has declared
OL,7,Fa critical incident after facing
OL,8,F'exceptionally high demand' in its
OL,9,Femergency departments - with some
OL,10,Fpatients waiting up to 50 hours on
OL,11,Ftrolleys in corridors for a bed.
OL,13,FThe NHS University Hospitals of
OL,14,FLiverpool Group made the announcement
OL,15,Fon Tuesday 7 January, urging people to
OL,16,Fconsider using other health services
OL,17,Fto "support the safe care and
OL,18,Ftreatment of our patients".
