OL,3,CHospital declares critical incident
OL,4,Cwith patients waiting up to 50 hours
OL,6,FThe statement on X said: "Due to high
OL,7,Fdemand on our Emergency Departments,
OL,8,Fwe have declared a critical incident
OL,9,Fat our Royal Liverpool University
OL,10,FHospital site."
OL,12,FThe hospital has also said that the
OL,13,Fnumber of patients being admitted to
OL,14,Fhospital wards in recent weeks,
OL,15,Fparticularly with the flu, Norovirus
OL,16,Fand respiratory illnesses, is also
OL,17,Fputting pressure on its services.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
