OL,3,CHospital declares critical incident
OL,4,Cwith patients waiting up to 50 hours
OL,6,FDr Jim Gardner, Chief Medical Officer
OL,7,Fat the Trust, said while patients are
OL,8,Fbeing seen "immediately" within the
OL,9,FA&E department, the pressures meant
OL,10,Fsome were then having to wait "a long
OL,11,Ftime" to be placed on a ward.
OL,13,F"Patients are not waiting to be seen
OL,14,Ffor that long," he said. "If anybody
OL,15,Fcomes who is poorly they will be seen
OL,16,Fstraight away but in order to then
OL,17,Fcare for them and move them on to
OL,18,Fhospital bed some people are then
OL,19,Fwaiting a long time to move through.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
