OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F394A1736294969
OL,3,CHospital declares critical incident
OL,4,Cwith patients waiting up to 50 hours
OL,6,F"They are being cared for but there
OL,7,Fare patients who are being cared for
OL,8,Fon trolleys in the emergency
OL,9,Fdepartment and on corridors but we try
OL,10,Fand give as much dignity to those
OL,11,Fpatients are we can and to look after
OL,12,Fthem as best we can, but it's not
OL,13,Fwhere anyone would want to have the
OL,14,Fbest care."
OL,16,FHe added it was "distressing for
OL,17,Fpatients and their families as well as
OL,18,Four staff who are doing their best".
