OL,6,FDr Jim Gardner, Chief Medical Officer
OL,7,Fat NHS University Hospitals of
OL,8,FLiverpool Group, says some patients
OL,9,Fare having to wait "a long time"
OL,11,FDr Gardner said some out-patient
OL,12,Fappointments and elective surgeries
OL,13,Fhad been cancelled because of the
OL,14,Fincident - but stressed those who are
OL,15,Faffected will be contacted.
