OL,3,CHospital declares critical incident
OL,4,Cwith patients waiting up to 50 hours
OL,6,F"In the hospital we are extremely busy
OL,7,Fat the moment," he said. "Yesterday we
OL,8,Fdeclared what's called an internal
OL,9,Fcritical incident because of a surge
OL,10,Fof patients suffering from flu-like
OL,11,Fillnesses who are poorly and being
OL,12,Fadmitted to hospitals, and more and
OL,13,Fmore our escalation areas have filled
OL,14,Fup, so we're having to move patients
OL,15,Finto further areas and begin to step
OL,16,Fdown some elective surgery and remove
OL,17,Fcolleagues from out patients and help
OL,18,Fpatients in accident and emergencies.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
