PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F394A1736294969
OL,3,CHospital declares critical incident
OL,4,Cwith patients waiting up to 50 hours
OL,6,F"It's a very busy environment, but if
OL,7,Fpeople are really poorly, there are
OL,8,Faccidents or medical emergencies
OL,9,Fpatients are being seen and of course
OL,10,Fwe will manage them accordingly."
OL,12,FDr Jim Gardner, Chief Medical Officer
OL,13,Fat NHS University Hospitals of
OL,14,FLiverpool Group, says the hospital is
OL,15,F"extremely busy"
OL,17,FThe hospital has said it has a
OL,18,F"comprehensive plan in place" and is
OL,19,Ftaking the necessary steps to manage
OL,20,Fthe situation affecting its staff and
OL,21,Fpatients.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
