OL,3,CHospital declares critical incident
OL,4,Cwith patients waiting up to 50 hours
OL,6,FDr Gardner said that the response to
OL,7,Fthe incident was "going well" but said
OL,8,Fthe hospital would most likely remain
OL,9,Fwithin the critical incident for a
OL,10,Fnumber of days due to the volume of
OL,11,Fpatients.
OL,13,FThe spokesperson added: "We are
OL,14,Fworking with partner organisations to
OL,15,Fensure those that are medically fit
OL,16,Fcan leave hospital safely and at the
OL,17,Fearliest opportunity.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
