OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F394A1736294969
OL,3,CHospital declares critical incident
OL,4,Cwith patients waiting up to 50 hours
OL,6,F"Colleagues are working incredibly
OL,7,Fhard to treat people as quickly as
OL,8,Fpossible, however some people will
OL,9,Fexperience longer waits while we treat
OL,10,Four sickest patients.
OL,12,F"If it is not a medical emergency
OL,13,Fplease consider using other services,
OL,14,Fsuch as your GP, local pharmacy or
OL,15,Fwalk-in centre.
OL,17,F"The NHS 111 service can be used to
OL,18,Fhelp identify the most appropriate
OL,19,Fservice for you and help avoid long
OL,20,Fwaits.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
